# Run state lives ONLY at the repo root (skillset-saves/). These patterns carry no
# leading slash, so they also catch a copy accidentally created deeper in the tree
# (e.g. app/skillset-saves/) — consolidate any such copy into the root one.
skillset-saves/
**/skillset-saves/

# --- build artifacts (CI rebuilds these; exe is ~80 MB) ---
app/dist/
app/frontend/dist/
app/frontend/node_modules/

